org.apache.river.outrigger.proxy

Class AdminProxy

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.river.outrigger.proxy.AdminProxy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, JoinAdmin, net.jini.id.ReferentUuid, DestroyAdmin, JavaSpaceAdmin
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ConstrainableAdminProxy

    public class AdminProxy
extends Object
implements JavaSpaceAdmin, net.jini.id.ReferentUuid, Serializable
    AdminProxy objects are connected to particular OutriggerServerImpls to implement the JavaSpaceAdmin interface for the server.
